Customer: Hello.

Executive: Ha yes sir, mai WhatsApp pe link send kar deti hu, thik hai? WhatsApp do. Meri senior, ya meri senior abhi aap connect kar loge na?
Customer: Ha connect karo.
Executive: Okay.
